high_descs: Turn right and walk to the dining table
Grab the apple on the table
Turn left, go to the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator, put the apple on the shelf below the shelf with a pan, close the refrigerator, open the refrigerator, take the apple out
Turn around and walk to the microwave
Open the microwave and put the apple in
anns.task_desc: Take the apple from the table, put it in the refrigerator, take it out, heat the apple in the microwave

high_descs: Pick up the apple from the table.
Bring the apple to the fridge.
Chill the apple in the fridge.
Bring the apple to the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple in the microwave.

high_descs: You have to turn away from the fridge to your right, rotate for three moves.
At the round table grab the red apple.
Take the apple traveling in left flank to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the apple on the shelf.
Take the apple back, before closing in the fridge door.
You have to take the apple into the microwave, where you close and press the red stamp button.
anns.task_desc: To take, choose and clear out an item like an human while on foot beat.
